# Setting up your tools

```
*  Install slack
*  Check if have a github account
*  Get git bash for windows machine
*  Get Visual studio code
*  Setup gitlab, ssh and pull the code
*  Setup github and push the code
*  Add plugins/extensions of Vs code
```

# Plugins and extensions for VS code

```

* Prettier
* color hightlighter
* Live Server
* Code Spell Checker
* Markdown Preview GitHub Styling
* vscode-icons

File -> Preferences -> Settings
* auto save -> onFocusChange
* default formatter -> select prettier
* compact folder -> uncheck
* format on save -> check
* Ctrl+ Shift + P  - Open command palette and search for Select default profile select bash or zsh
```
